node.text: This sleeping beauty is 3 months old today! @summermoon

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Scheana on July 23, 2021 tagging @houseofcb, @kylechandesign, @brock__davies, and @bespoke_balloons_studio. May be an image of 2 people, people kissing, balloon and text that says 'Marry me'.

node.text: I SAID YES!!!!! 💍 We are engaged!!! Thank you to @brock__davies for making me the happiest girl in the world and to @kylechandesign for making me the most gorgeous ring ever!! Tune in to an all new episode of @scheananigans to hear the story and watch our video podcast on patreon to see the ring! #itsallhappening 💍🤍

node.text: Summer is one lucky girl! @brock__davies you are the most amazing, hands on and loving father I could ever ask for for our daughter. From day one @summermoon has felt love and comfort from you. You can clearly see where her happy place is (and it’s mine too) Happy Father’s Day honey!!!
